public class A {

    public String sayHello(String name) {
        return "Hello " + name;
    }

}

public class B {
    @Delegate
    private A a = new A();

    public String sayHello2(String name) {
        return sayHello(name) + ". My name is Malvin.";
    }
}

i can use directly the function of another in class in sprinboot by using this lombok @delegate annotation in java